{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以\"绝人绝事\"为题，展现两个核心场景。马如龙与大婉来到停尸验尸之处，却见江南俞五正为一位穿红衣的老太婆梳头。老太婆虽年迈却一头乌黑长发，对俞五的手艺赞不绝口，称其若武功有梳头一半好便可天下无敌。俞五淡然回应，表示无敌于天下太过无趣。老太婆大笑，许诺即便不梳头也会帮俞五做事。随后大婉带马如龙去看一幅画，画中人是城中杂货铺老板张荣发——一个忠厚平凡的中年人。大婉详细介绍了张荣发的身世，然后语出惊人：马如龙就是张荣发，他很快会被易容成此人。马如龙虽觉荒谬，但从大婉的认真态度看出并非玩笑。最后大婉揭示俞五梳头的老太婆的真实身份——她姓玉，正是六十年前的\"玲珑玉手\"玉玲珑，一位活了一百八十岁仍是大小姐气度的传奇人物。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你能猜得出他在于什么，我佩服你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不要你佩服，我猜不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他在梳头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "没有人比得上你，绝对没有人比得上你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "只要你的武功有你梳头的本事一半好，你已经天下无敌。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "text": "幸好我并不想天下无敌。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "text": "因为一个人如果真的无敌于天下，日子过得一定很无趣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我喜欢你，真的喜欢你，就算你不替我梳头，我也会替你做这件事的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在你一定越来越胡涂了，因为你根本不知道我想干什么。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你还想干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我还想带你去看一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "这次是去看谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "看一个画在纸上的人，你就算比现在更聪明一百倍，也绝对猜不出这个人是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他姓张，叫张荣发，是个非常非常忠厚老实的人，在城里开了一间小杂货铺，用了一个跟他差不多老实忠诚的伙计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "今年他已经四十四岁，生肖是属猪的，十九岁时他就已娶亲，他的老婆叫桂枝，又会生气，又会生病，就是不会生孩子，所以越气越病，最近已经病得根本下不了床，连吃饭都要老张喂她，所以越气越病，脾气越来越大，连左右邻居都已受不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你听清楚没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "难道这个人跟我也有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "有一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我怎么会跟他有关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为这个人就是你，你就是他，他就是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "这个叫张荣发的人，就是我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "绝对是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他看起来一点都不像我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "但是你很快就会变得像他了，非常非常的像，甚至可以说完全一模一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可惜我不会变。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不会变，有人会替你变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你知不知道俞五为什么会替那位大小姐梳头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那位大小姐好像已经不是小姐了，好像已经是位老婆婆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她不是老婆婆，她是大小姐，有些人，就算活到一百八十岁，也一样是大小姐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她就是这种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "绝对是，如果她不是，世上就没有这种人了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为她姓玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她跟六十年前的那位玉大小姐有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她就是那位玉大小姐，她就是'玲珑玉手'玉玲珑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    }
  ],
